$3 \times \frac{1}{2} \times 950 \times (1.397 - 1.335)^2 \times 10^{-20} = 3 \times \frac{1}{2} \times 950 \times (0.062)^2 \times 10^{-20} = 3 \times 475 \times 0.003844 \times 10^{-20} = 5.4783 \times 10^{-20} \, \text{J}$.

